<br>
Basically if you protect your cleric and he gets hit for 100, he'll only take 50 and you'll take 75.<br>
<br>
This is very similar to the &quot;block&quot; move that they have in DAoC.  You target someone (often a spellcaster) and hit your block key to absorb a blow directed at them. <p><b>Enedlithien<BR>
